OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775481061
OL,3,C'Brutal' ball game with no rules
OL,4,Creturns to Cumbrian town
OL,6,FAn "absolutely brutal" ball game with
OL,7,Fno rules is returning to West Cumbria
OL,8,Ffor 2026.
OL,10,FThe 'Uppies and Downies' is played
OL,11,Fevery Easter in Workington, and pits
OL,12,Fthe upper part of the town against the
OL,13,Flower side.
OL,15,FThere are no rules, and players
OL,16,Fwrestle and scrum to get hold of the
OL,17,Fball and, with the aim of 'hailing it'
OL,18,F- to take it back to their end of the
OL,19,Ftown.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
