FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775481061
OL,3,C'Brutal' ball game with no rules
OL,4,Creturns to Cumbrian town
OL,6,FLeslie Saffill, whose family has
OL,7,Fsponsored the ball since 1985, said:
OL,8,F"Whether you're young or old, it's
OL,9,Fabsolutely brutal, but it's fantastic
OL,10,Fto be involved in."
OL,12,FHer family got involved when her
OL,13,Ffather bought a local pub, and the
OL,14,Fresponsibility of throwing the ball in
OL,15,Fthe air to start the game has been
OL,16,Fhanded down to different family
OL,17,Fmembers over the generations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775481061
OL,3,C'Brutal' ball game with no rules
OL,4,Creturns to Cumbrian town
OL,6,FLeslie said: "It's important because
OL,7,Fof the history - it's dated back that
OL,8,Flong that they can't actually put a
OL,9,Fdate for when it started.
OL,11,F"We do have a bit of banter because my
OL,12,Fmum and dad are Uppies, but me, my
OL,13,Fhusband and my children are Downies so
OL,14,Fwe do have a laugh."
OL,16,FDarcie, who is 16, has been trusted to
OL,17,Fstart the game in past years, but has
OL,18,Fsince passed on that role to her
OL,19,Fyounger cousin.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775481061
OL,3,C'Brutal' ball game with no rules
OL,4,Creturns to Cumbrian town
OL,6,FShe said: "People have been going on
OL,7,Fabout it since it turned January.
OL,8,FEveryone's been saying: 'it's nearly
OL,9,FUppies and Downies' and now it's here,
OL,10,Fso everyone's just ready and excited
OL,11,Fto come down.
OL,13,F"You just talk to everyone and it's a
OL,14,Fgood way of getting the whole town
OL,15,Ftogether and just having a
OL,16,Fconversation with people you haven't
OL,17,Ftalked to."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
