PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775481061
OL,3,C'Brutal' ball game with no rules
OL,4,Creturns to Cumbrian town
OL,6,FThere are three matches played every
OL,7,Fyear, with the first on Good Friday
OL,8,Fand the next on the following Tuesday
OL,9,Fand Saturday.
OL,11,FEach match is played until there is a
OL,12,Fwinner, and can last multiple days.
OL,14,FIn 2025, the Uppies won all three
OL,15,Fmatches.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
